INSERT INTO `oc_setting` VALUES(10725, 0, 'welcome', 'welcome_module', 'a:1:{i:1;a:5:{s:11:"description";a:2:{i:1;s:4842:"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px&quot;&gt;Inspire enquiry and order hotline: 3757 8065 /&amp;nbsp;9303 0021&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;[September&amp;nbsp;16]&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;Trick or Treat!!! Halloween is coming soon~ Please visit our Facebook page to buy some lovely Halloween costume for your baby now&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[August 29] &lt;/strong&gt;New item release: Disney Baby stroller/ car seat headrest and Hello Kitty Baby utensils and bathroom accessories&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px&quot;&gt;[August 18]&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;The 1st lot of baby blanket has been sold out (HKD65.0 each), the 2nd lot of the blanket will be ready this week.....&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px&quot;&gt;[August 4]&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Inspire VIP members can enjoy the special offer this month!! Vtech&amp;nbsp;Hello Kitty Playmat Cube at special price HK$699 (Original price: HK$749) Only 5 boxes are available. Act quick before all sold~&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[July 23]&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Our WhatsApp account is being launched now! Please feel free to add 9303 0021 for any enquires or place order.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px&quot;&gt;[July 20] &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px&quot;&gt;Welcome to join the membership of Inspire. Just input your personal information once and no need to re-enter the information again for your future purchases. You can also check the old purchasing record in your profile and receive our promotion newsletter in advance! In the meantime, you can use also Pay Pal service for any purchase over HK$400.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[July 17] &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;We are pleased to announced that Inspire toy store is going to&amp;nbsp;have some &quot;Skip Hop&quot; products in our FB page and online shopping store. You are welcome to visit our &quot;Baby Bed Accessories&quot; section to find out more informaton.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[July 2] &lt;/strong&gt;Merries diapers are available at Inspire now!!!&amp;nbsp;Mommy&amp;nbsp;and dadddy can&amp;nbsp;purchase directly through&amp;nbsp;our official website or facebook. Our Merries diapers are originally&amp;nbsp;imported from&amp;nbsp;Japan and the quality is assured!&amp;nbsp;You are always welcomed to contact us at 3757 8065 to check the available stock.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[June 23] &lt;/strong&gt;Sanrio Hello Kitty Babies products are available now!!! All are made in&amp;nbsp;Japan or&amp;nbsp;Taiwan, Hello Kitty Mommy Fans should not missed the lovely baby products~&amp;nbsp;You can visit&amp;nbsp;&quot;Hello Kitty&amp;nbsp;Specials&quot; page in our website to&amp;nbsp;view all Baby Kitty products with our BEST promotion price~ During the promotion period, if you&amp;nbsp;buy over HK$280, you can&amp;nbsp;enjoy FREE shipping (HK only)!!!!&amp;nbsp;We will keep&amp;nbsp;updating&amp;nbsp;the products&amp;nbsp;regularly, so please&amp;nbsp;keep an eye on &quot;Hello Kitty Specials&quot; page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[June 18] &lt;/strong&gt;Welcome to visit our Facebook page &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.facebook.com/inspiretoystore/&quot;&gt;http://www.facebook.com/inspiretoystore/&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;We will update the content daily, and&amp;nbsp;offer the latest discounts to our facebook fans. Please&amp;nbsp;remember to &quot;Like&quot; &amp;amp; &quot;Share&quot; Inspire Toy Store Facebook page in order to get the hottest and latest promotion~&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[Good news for Macao residents]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n*** We have opened bank account in Macau, so that will make mommy and daddy in Macau to go shopping with Inspire more conveniently. There would be no more headache to pay high transaction cost now!&amp;nbsp;You can go online shopping through our website, it will automatically caculate the freight charge wirh you check-out. Simply deposit the payment to our bank account and the products would be shipped to your home right away.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;[June 6]&lt;/strong&gt; We are proud to announce that INSPIRE Toys Store''s official website is launched!!! &lt;a href=&quot;http://nspire.hk/&quot;&gt;http://nspire.hk/&lt;/a&gt; The interface is very user friendly and easy to navigate. In addition to Bank-in transfer payment, or pay by cash,&amp;nbsp;PayPal checkout is also available too!&amp;nbsp;We hope you will enjoy shopping at Inspire~&lt;/p&gt;\r\n";i:2;s:4305:"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inspire查詢或訂貨熱線: 3757 8065 /&amp;nbsp;9303 0021&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;【9月16日】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;&quot;&gt;下個月又到扮鬼扮馬嘅萬聖節喇~ 可愛嘅小寶寶點可以錯過呢個機會打扮一下, 應下節呢? Inspire推出萬聖節嬰兒和小童夾衣, 頭飾等用品, 等媽媽唔駛周圍撲, 買返幾件去開Halloween Party啦~!!!! 最新優惠可到&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;www.facebook.com/inspiretoystore&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【8月29日】&lt;/strong&gt;新返Disney小熊維尼嬰兒護頸墊, Hello Kitty 特色貨品&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【8月18日】&lt;/strong&gt;第一批BB冷氣包被&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px&quot;&gt;(每張&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px&quot;&gt;優惠價HK$65)&lt;/span&gt;已經全部售罊喇!! 第二批將會在本週送到......&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【8月4日】&lt;/strong&gt;8月份大優惠~ Vtech Hello Kitty 2合1音樂方塊遊戲墊會員專享優惠價HK$699!!! (原價HK$749) 只限5件, 售完即止~&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【7月23日】&lt;/strong&gt; Inspire開通WhatsApp功能喇~!! 大家可隨時隨地發短訊到9303 0021查詢或訂貨, 購物更方便容易!!!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【7月20日】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;userContent&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;歡迎大家成為Inspire的會員, 只須輸入一次資料, 以後每次購物就不用再重新&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;輸入所有資料, 而且更可查閱舊有消費記錄, 又可以優先收到Inspire最新的優惠通訊呢!!&amp;nbsp;另外, 大家在Inspire官網購物, 只需買滿HK$400或以上, 就可以用PayPal結賬喇~&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【7月17日】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;userContent&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;有見市場對Skip Hop產品需求日漸增加, Inspire 已經嚴選了一些高品質和富有教育意義的產品, 大家可到嬰兒床上用品中瀏覽&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【7月2日】&lt;/strong&gt;今次又有好消息喇~ 各位爸爸媽媽可以透過Inspire facebook或官網http://nspire.hk/ 去訂購Merries尿片呢!!! 我哋仲推出限時特平優惠價, 希望大家多多支持, 歡迎留言查詢~~&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br type=&quot;_moz&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;【6月23日】&lt;/strong&gt;店主已經成功傾到Sanrio Hello Kitty Baby嬰兒用品返嚟喇~!!! 全部是原裝日本、台灣貨, 相信今次又令所有Kitty媽媽Fans愛不釋手~ ^.^~ 大家可以去 「Hello Kitty專頁」, 就可以瀏覽所有Baby Kitty的產品, 價錢保證比市價平宜!!! 我們同時推出大優惠, 只要買滿HK$280即時免運費 !!!! (只限香港地區) 我們定時會更新及增加更多產品, 大家記得密切留意喔~&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【6月18日】&lt;/strong&gt;歡迎瀏覽我們Facebook的專頁 &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.facebook.com/inspiretoystore/&quot;&gt;www.facebook.com/inspiretoystore/&lt;/a&gt; 我們會每日定期更新內容, 並推出最新折扣優惠, 大家記得去「Like/讚好」&amp;amp; 「Share/分享」INSPIRE嬰兒用品及玩具網上專頁啦!!!!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【澳門居民好消息】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n***我們已經開通了澳門的銀行賬戶了, 各位澳門爸爸媽媽以後購物更方便, 網上結算時會自動幫你計運費, 只須過數到Inspire的賬號, 我們便會馬上速遞到府上。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em&quot;&gt;【6月6日】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em&quot;&gt;INSPIRE嬰兒用品及玩具網上專門店的官網正式面世喇!!! http://nspire.hk/ 介面簡單容易瀏覽, 方便各位直接於網上購物, 除了Bank-in和面交現金, 更可用PayPal結賬 (*需購物滿HK$400或以上), 結賬時同時計算運費呢! 非常直接快捷方便~~&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n";}s:9:"layout_id";s:1:"1";s:8:"position";s:11:"content_top";s